      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t買部esim 美版iphone 15 + esim數據漫游data roaming應該可以，只是成本非常高，一個月可能要100鎂以上<br/>\n<br/>\namazon有0.01鎂購機的plan，sim locked，要簽36個月合約，每個月月費60鎂，也許可以在中國使用<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1pUGhvbmUtUHJvLU1heC10cmFkZS9kcC9CMENIQlE5Mkgx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-iPhone-Pro-Max-trade/dp/B0CHBQ92H1\">https://www.amazon.com/Apple-iPhone-Pro-Max-trade/dp/B0CHBQ92H1</a> </div>",
